metadata.name: Love Paris
metadata.description:
I have always been an observer of the world where humans are the heart of my work.

During all my travels, I like to feed on the secret and moments of the people around me.

Through my eyes, I perceive them with my "filter of humanism" and reflect them to you with my own
emotions.

Everyone can find themselves in my work, find a piece of themselves and their own story.

Unconsciously they will invite you to recall some "not so important" memories and help you revive them.

It will encourage you to start your own inner journey and help you enjoy the moment.

--------------------------------------

Can also sell real wire art version.
